        "title": "SERVING SUGGESTION",
        "detail-box-txt": "<p>This wine will complement spicy food such as Thai-style green curries, or Indian kormas. It will also pair well with sushi and sashimi as well as pasta served with a carbonara or a puttanesca sauce.</p>",
